                            <comment id="16216497" author="krummas" created="Tue, 24 Oct 2017 08:06:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch LGTM, but I think the message could be a bit clearer that we don&apos;t support mixed version repairs - not sure &quot;messaging service version&quot; is something that makes sense to end users. Adding something like &quot;make sure all nodes involved in the repair are on the same major version&quot; to the message might help?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
